data.description: Stop in and take a tour of this prime location, a stunning, traditional-style home in the thriving sought-after Greenwood Forest community, conveniently located near FM-1960, local hospitals, and IAH airport! This family-friendly floorplan includes four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, a large family room, and a spacious kitchen. A recent upstairs renovation features beautiful aqua guard life-proof luxury vinyl planking throughout. This beautiful, bright layout includes 2021, 30-year roof replacement, double-pane windows, up-to-date AC service, and a large backyard, making this home great for a first-time home buyer or a new family looking for more room!
